+| `reflect>` prompt after hand | `crates/myosu-tui/src/pipe.rs` | Slice 4 | **MISSING** |
+| `GameState` JSON schema | `crates/myosu-tui/src/schema.rs` | — | **TRUSTED** (16 tests) |
+| `docs/api/game-state.json` | `docs/api/game-state.json` | — | **TRUSTED** |
+
