+| `--narrate` flag wiring | `crates/myosu-tui/src/pipe.rs` | Slice 6 | **MISSING** |
+| Lobby + `info` command | `crates/myosu-tui/src/pipe.rs` | Slice 7 | **MISSING** |
+
+### Phase 2 (depends on `play:tui` binary, Slice 1 of that lane)
